welcome:
🎉Welcome to Mr.Instagram Robot🎉
Well, here you can start👇
getAccount:
📲To work with this section you need to log in to the Account.

⚙️All you have to do is send me your username and password like this:
account:Username:Password

💡For example, our username is Googel and the password is 123456. We should send it this way:👇

account:Googel:123456
sussesAcoount: Your account has been successfully connected✅
inValideAccount:
😓Sorry, I could not connect to the account❌
💡Please try again by checking your account information.
ErrorAccount:
🙁You have not added an account yet.
💡Use the button below to return to the previous page and go to the account management section and add an account.
GetUserFollow:
💼Well, now send me the username of the person in question like this👇:
follow@username
For example👇:
follow@afsh7n_
GetUserLike:
💼Well, now send me the Link Post of the person in question like this👇:
like@linkPost
For example👇:
like@https://www.instagram.com/p/CJq-B_RMRv4/?igshid=pvd70120paid

💡If you want to know how to get the post link, click on this command:👇
/help_linkPost
GetUserUnFollow:
💼Well, now send me the username of the person in question like this👇:
unfollow@username
For example👇:
unfollow@afsh7n_
GetUserUnlike:
💼Well, now send me the Link Post of the person in question like this👇:
unlike@linkPost
For example👇:
unlike@https://www.instagram.com/p/CJq-B_RMRv4/?igshid=pvd70120paid

💡If you want to know how to get the post link, click on this command:👇
/help_linkPost
